1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,329
One day, I stopped in to see an old business friend.
2
00:00:03,600 --> 00:00:07,490
She had just returned from a conference with several of her executives.
3
00:00:07,680 --> 00:00:12,769
The moment I looked at her, I could tell there was something she wanted to get off her chest.
4
00:00:13,039 --> 00:00:16,529
She had the look of a woman who had suffered real disappointment.
5
00:00:16,880 --> 00:00:24,130
You know," she said, I called that conference this morning because I wanted some help on a proposed policy change.
6
00:00:24,320 --> 00:00:26,289
But what kind of help did I get?
7
00:00:26,480 --> 00:00:31,170
I had six men in there, and only one of them had anything to contribute.
8
00:00:31,440 --> 00:00:36,289
Two others talked, but what they said was just an echo of what I had said.
9
00:00:36,480 --> 00:00:39,250
It was like talking with a bunch of vegetables.
10
00:00:39,519 --> 00:00:43,410
I confess it's hard for me to find out what those fellows think.
11
00:00:43,840 --> 00:00:49,650
Really, she went on, you'd think those fellows would speak up and let me know what they think.
12
00:00:49,840 --> 00:00:52,850
After all, it directly affects each of them.
13
00:00:53,840 --> 00:00:56,610
My friend didn't get help in the conference.
14
00:00:56,720 --> 00:01:03,089
But had you roamed the hall after the meeting broke up, you'd have heard her junior associates making remarks like,
15
00:01:03,440 --> 00:01:08,370
I felt like saying, why didn't someone suggest, I don't think,
16
00:01:08,560 --> 00:01:10,210
we ought to go ahead.
17
00:01:10,640 --> 00:01:15,569
So, often the vegetables, those who have nothing to say in the conference room,
18
00:01:15,600 --> 00:01:20,850
are full of talk after the meeting, when what they've got to say won't make any difference.
19
00:01:20,880 --> 00:01:24,130
They're suddenly full of life when it's too late.
20
00:01:25,279 --> 00:01:27,890
Business executives want comment.
21
00:01:28,080 --> 00:01:31,890
The fellow who hides his light under a bushel hurts himself.
22
00:01:32,560 --> 00:01:34,450
Get the speak-up habit.
